## ğŸ’¡ About This Project

This dashboard was built for **Abheshu Pharma** to simulate and support strategic decisions in global pharmaceutical sourcing. It reflects how I would think and operate as an **Associate Manager â€“ Global Sourcing** by turning supplier data into action.

It tackles critical pain points in sourcing APIs (Active Pharmaceutical Ingredients), RLDs (Reference Listed Drugs), FDFs (Finished Dosage Forms), and comparator drugs â€” all through a data-driven lens.

